'''佩羅鱷科'''（Peirosauridae）是[[中真鱷類|中真鱷類]]的一科，生存於[[白堊紀|白堊紀]]晚期的南方各大陸。佩羅鱷科是群陸生、[[肉食性|肉食性]]鱷類，外形接近[[狗|狗]]。根據2004年的[[種系發生學|種系發生學]]定義，佩羅鱷科的範圍包含：[[佩羅鱷|佩羅鱷]]與洛馬鱷亞科的最近共同祖先，與其最近共同祖先的所有後代<ref name="Carvalho et al., 2004">{{cite journal |last=Carvalho |first=I.S. |coauthors=Ribeiro, L.C.B.; and Avilla, L.S. |year=2004 |title=''Uberabasuchus terrificus'' sp. nov., a new Crocodylomorpha from the Bauru Basin (Upper Cretaceous), Brazil |journal=Gondwana Research |volume=7 |issue=4 |pages=975–1002 |url=http://acd.ufrj.br/ismar/3/3_15.pdf |doi=10.1016/S1342-937X(05)71079-0 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110706162632/http://acd.ufrj.br/ismar/3/3_15.pdf |archivedate=2011-07-06 |access-date=2008-10-10 }}</ref>。

在2004年的同份研究，在佩羅鱷科內建立洛馬鱷亞科（Lomasuchinae），範圍包含：[[洛馬鱷|洛馬鱷]]、馬任加鱷族（Mahajangasuchini）的最近共同祖先，與其最近共同祖先的所有後代。而馬任加鱷族的範圍包含：[[馬任加鱷|馬任加鱷]]、[[烏貝拉巴鱷|烏貝拉巴鱷]]的最近共同祖先，與其最近共同祖先的所有後代<ref name="Carvalho et al., 2004"/>。但根據2009年的[[種系發生學|種系發生學]]研究，馬任加鱷不屬於佩羅鱷科，而屬於[[馬任加鱷科|馬任加鱷科]]；馬任加鱷科還包含新屬[[野豬鱷|野豬鱷]]（''Kaprosuchus''）<ref name=SL09>{{cite journal |last=Sereno |first=P. C. |coauthors=and Larsson, H. C. E. |year=2009 |title=Cretaceous crocodyliforms from the Sahara |journal=ZooKeys |volume=28 |issue=2009 |pages=1–143 |url=http://pensoftonline.net/zookeys/index.php/journal/article/view/325 |author= |access-date=2012-04-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100921055501/http://pensoftonline.net/zookeys/index.php/journal/article/view/325 |archive-date=2010-09-21 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。因此，洛馬鱷亞科目前僅包含洛馬鱷屬。

==屬==
*[[佩羅鱷|佩羅鱷]]（''Peirosaurus''）：生存於[[馬斯垂克階|馬斯垂克階]]晚期的[[巴西|巴西]]<ref name="Candeiro et al., 2006">Candeiro CRA, Martinelli AG, Avilla LS, Rich TH. 2006. Tetrapods from the Upper Cretaceous (Turonian-Maastrichtian) Bauru Group of Brazil: a reappraisal. ''Cretaceous Research'' '''27''' (6): 923-946.</ref>。
*[[洛馬鱷|洛馬鱷]]（''Lomasuchus''）：生存於[[阿根廷|阿根廷]]，年代為[[桑托階|桑托階]]<ref name="Carvalho et al., 2004"/>。
*[[烏貝拉巴鱷|烏貝拉巴鱷]]（''Uberasuchus''）：生存於馬斯垂克階晚期的巴西<ref name="Carvalho et al., 2004"/><ref name="Candeiro et al., 2006"/>。
*[[蒙特阿爾托鱷|蒙特阿爾托鱷]]（''Montealtosuchus''）：生存於[[土侖階|土侖階]]到[[桑托階|桑托階]]的巴西<ref name="Carvalho et al., 2007">Carvalho IS, Vasconcellos FM, Tavares SAS. 2007. ''Montealtosuchus arrudacamposi'', a new peirosaurid crocodile (Mesoeucrocodylia) from the Late Cretaceous Adamantina Formation of Brazil. ''Zootaxa'' '''1607''': 35–46</ref>。
*[[哈米德鱷|哈米德鱷]] ''Hamadasuchus''：生存於[[阿爾比階|阿爾比階]]到[[坎潘階|坎潘階]]的[[摩洛哥|摩洛哥]]。
*''Barcinosuchus''：生存於[[阿普第階|阿普第階]]到[[阿爾比階|阿爾比階]]的[[阿根廷|阿根廷]]<ref name="Leardi09">{{Cite journal|author=Juan Martín Leardi and Diego Pol |year=2009 |title=The first crocodyliform from the Chubut Group (Chubut Province, Argentina) and its phylogenetic position within basal Mesoeucrocodylia |url= |journal=Cretaceous Research |volume=30 |issue=6 |pages=1376–1386 |doi=10.1016/j.cretres.2009.08.002}}</ref>。
*''Gasparinisuchus''：生存於[[桑托階|桑托階]]到[[坎潘階|坎潘階]]的[[阿根廷|阿根廷]]<ref name=Gasparinisuchus>{{cite journal |author=Agustín G. Martinelli, Joseph J.W. Sertich, Alberto C. Garrido and Ángel M. Praderio |year=2012 |title=A new peirosaurid from the Upper Cretaceous of Argentina: Implications for specimens referred to ''Peirosaurus torminni'' Price (Crocodyliformes: Peirosauridae) |journal=Cretaceous Research |volume=in press |pages= |doi=10.1016/j.cretres.2012.03.017}}</ref>。 
*''Pepesuchus''：生存於[[坎潘階|坎潘階]]到[[馬斯垂克階|馬斯垂克階]]的[[巴西|巴西]]<ref name=Pepesuchus>{{cite journal |last=Campos |first=Diogenes A. |coauthors=Gustavo R. Oliveira, Rodrigo G. Figueiredo, Douglas Riff, Sergio A.K. Azevedo, Luciana B. Carvalho and Alexander W.A. Kellner |year=2011 |title=On a new peirosaurid crocodyliform from the Upper Cretaceous, Bauru Group, southeastern Brazil |url=http://www.scielo.br/pdf/aabc/v83n1/v83n1a20.pdf |journal=Anais da Academia Brasileira de Ciências |volume=83 |issue=1 |pages=317–327 |doi=10.1590/S0001-37652011000100020 |access-date=2012-04-03 |archive-date=2019-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190303215100/http://www.scielo.br/pdf/aabc/v83n1/v83n1a20.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
*''Bayomesasuchus''：生存於[[土仑階|土仑階]]到[[森諾曼階|森諾曼階]]的[[阿根廷|阿根廷]]<ref name=Bayomesasuchus>{{cite journal |author1=Francisco Barrios, Ariana Paulina-Carabajal  |author2=Paula Bona  |lastauthoramp=yes |year=2015 |title=A new peirosaurid (Crocodyliformes, Mesoeucrocodylia) from the Upper Cretaceous of Patagonia, Argentina |journal=Ameghiniana |volume=in press |issue= |pages= 14–25|doi=10.5710/AMGH.03.09.2015.2903 }}</ref>。
*''Barrosasuchus''：生存於[[桑托阶|桑托阶]]的[[阿根廷|阿根廷]]。
*''Caririsuchuss''：生存於[[阿普第階|阿普第階]]到[[阿爾比階|阿爾比階]]的[[巴西|巴西]]<ref name=Caririsuchus>C. F. C. Geroto and R. J. Bertini. 2018. [https://www.researchgate.net/publicati/326131825_New_material_of_Pepesuchus_Crocodyliformes_Mesoeucrocodylia_from_the_Bauru_Group_implications_about_its_phylogeny_and_the_age_of_the_Adamantina_Formation/ New material of Pepesuchus (Crocodyliformes; Mesoeucrocodylia) from the Bauru Group: implications about its phylogeny and the age of the Adamantina Formation]. Zoological Journal of the Linnean Society 185(2):312-334</ref>.

